overview: Casey brings over 25 years of corporate management and business development experience to VSee Labs. Casey’s career includes leadership positions in National Sales, Marketing and Regional Operations at Citibank, US Bank and Lehman Brothers. For over 8 years, Casey was the President of a niche consulting agency responsible for building national sales platforms for Lenders and Wall Street firms. Casey is a graduate of The United States Military Academy at West Point and the Graduate School of Bank Management at the University of Colorado, Boulder.
